This is "Automatic NWChem Compilation v.2" for installing NWChem program package
on RHEL and CentOS with single (OpenMP) and parallel (MPI) methods.

For more details, please visit the following websites

1. https://github.com/rangsimanketkaew/NWChem
2. https://sites.google.com/site/rangsiman1993/comp-chem/program-install/install-nwchem-rhel-centos

